  "texts": [
    "One day, a group of children playing near Jonah's booth caught his attention.",
    "They were laughing and",
    "The bush withered, and Jonah was left standing in the scorching heat, feeling dejected and frustrated.",
    "His protests and arguments with God seemed fruitless, and he couldn't help but wonder if all his efforts had been futile.",
    "As he pondered this, a group of Ninevites approached him."
  ]
